      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Lubricate the steer axle king pins, total of four fittings. Two
on the right side and two on the left side.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Lubricate the steering link bearings, total of four fittings.
Two on the right side and two on the left side.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Check for any worn or loose components of the steering mechanism. Remove any debris or
        trash as required. </p>
            <p>
               <p>
                  <fig id="fig_zwy_3yz_5gc">
